	(text "Cl := 12.5pF\n\nlet Cparasitic = 2pF\nC1 = 2(12.5pF - 2pF) = 20pF\n\nlet Cparasitic = 5pF\nC1 = 2(12.5pF - 5pF) = 14pF\n\npick C1 = 17pF"
